i miss my best friend i miss my everything i miss my snugglebear i miss the butterflies i miss your eyes i miss having you i miss laying in your arms all day i miss unconditional love i miss ((trying)) to be there for you i miss being the one you came to i miss running through the sprinklers ((hehe)) i miss the christmas lights i miss being complete i miss only needing you i miss crying on the phone all night i miss how you made it all better i miss how you made me feel beautiful i miss the way youd kiss my puffy cheeks i miss the way youd make fun of me i miss being tucked in i miss the way you took care of me i miss sweet november i miss the late night phone calls i miss the perfect silence i miss making up i miss knowing you wanted to i miss our first moments i miss our innocence i miss the passion i miss the cookies i miss my big stuffed bear i miss crying in your arms i miss pooh bear and eeyore i miss being held i miss how safe it felt sometimes i miss our purity i miss flowers on my doorstep i miss the way we could never stay mad i miss how we knew the fights didnt even matter i miss being worth it i miss how the parties were an inconvenience that merely distracted us from each other i miss always wanting to be alone ((with you)) i miss lying to my mom every night and day so i could see you i miss how you made time disappear i miss our conversations i miss knowing youd call back every time i hung up i miss saying "i love you" atleast 200 times before leaving for 2 minutes i miss fighting if wed say "love you" without the i i miss the way youd always find a way for us to be together i miss being your girlfriend i miss our sleepovers i miss the way you kissed me i miss how it was a perfect match i miss my "back rubs" i miss kisses on the belly button i miss how wed put up with each other i miss hiding from your parents i miss the way youd make me blush i miss the way you thought everything was cute i miss how we didnt give a fuck who told us we shouldnt be together i miss how we were in love i miss how much we wanted to work things out i miss how we never gave up i miss the way you saw me i miss the way i saw you i miss less than jake i miss always finding a way to hide from everyone else simply because were the only ones who mattered i miss konstantine i miss meaning the words i say i miss who you were i miss who i was i miss us i miss my forever i miss the way you missed it.

i went and put down flowers and by the end of the day my face was covered in black i guess its just my turn to be worried and cry endlessly over the people i love and the friends im so fucking scared of losing i will never touch a drug i will always remember today

i dont hate alex. me and logan talked signed some "seperation papers" went to dinner and i love her more than ever. i guess we just realized that no matter how far apart and different we may be, we arent obligated to keep this friendship together. were best friends. i guess its just harder to break us than we thought. i was so sad. so hurt but now im happier than ever. i love you loggy <3

someone wipe this smile off my face

because its been imprinted here all day.

you dont see the harm in this try to ignore the changes in my voice when my eyes start to water im just going to look away like i always do close my eyes and pretend this isnt happening. pretend i never loved you. pretend i never lost you pretend you never lost me pretend you were never there to begin with. i guess sometimes i wish i didnt care just so i could stand by your side smiling. youll neglect to realize this is even about you that youre the only person who matters enough to ever make me cry its sad youre the person who i yearn to be closest to and the one who needs to stay the farthest away i wish i could keep pretending you dont matter that i could stop writing this now i dont want you knowing how i love you its better left unsaid it was never enough to make you want to change i was never enough to make you want to stay. just pretend you never knew me what id give to wish you away and for once say it with sincerity. if only i wasnt still shaking from all the pain you kissed away ((.i love the circle we spin, where kisses burn holes only you can fill.)) im the only one left broken by this im the one who forgot how to love i want to be able to love you to look you in the eyes and let myself melt again im too tired to hold myself up simply so i wont fall down at your feet i hate myself for missing a dream we never lived up to most of all i hate that youll never change not because you arent strong enough but because you're too happy to see the need i wish you would give anything for me and want this the way i did i wish just once i could lay in your arms and not feel my heart pulling out of my chest running away because thats all i can ever do. i hate feeling that fear only love can burn knowing the only consequence of floating is crashing to the ground that much harder most of all i hate how the only cure for a broken heart is falling in love with you all over again. my eyes will always sparkle my heart will always melt and i will always miss you. that just isnt enough

im so fucking tired right now.. and that goes so far beyond getting three hours of sleep last night. im sick of my mood swings and the constant confusion with with my life. i can be so happy and then next day my entire world feels meaningless. its getting old. this time its about me wanting someone the way i havent in so long. and needing more than nothing.

yeah.. its cool how i love nicole more than anything, and she doesnt fucking see that... i do stupid shit, we got into different things, but despite that she means the fucking world to me and she always will. weve been best friends since 7th grade.. and it seems like its all falling apart.. i dont want to fucking lose her.. i mean it when i say i love her more than fucking anything. no matter what happens i would always put her before anything, and im sorry that no one seems to see that. shit gets fucked up sometimes, and i just dont know how to fix it.. whatever i love you nicole.. i know you dont even read this shit but whatever.. just know how much you mean to me.. and if i dont show that then im a fucking asshole but it has nothing to do with you or how much i care about you.. youll always come before anything else, i just dont want to put you in awkard situations sometimes... I LOVE YOU.. byee <33

THERE IS SO MUCH I NEED TO SAY TO YOU BUT I CANT BRING MYSELF TO SPEAK. ... i dont want you to know. i come so close sometimes to saying everything and then turning away forever but i know i can never completely walk away from this and i dont want to be around when you know whats truly going through my head.

im like the little monkey from outbreak.



hahaha.

im sick of caring.

these knots in my stomach arent butterflies anymore.

Everyone should do this on my comments: i ____ Jennie. Jennie is ______. if i were alone in a room with Jennie, i would _______. i think Jennie should _____. Jennie needs ______. i want to ____________Jennie. haha i feel so gay doing that.. but its ok, cause logan did it first. <3 my appoligies to whoever calls me.. i stopped answering my phone.. i do enjoy your messages though =) i went to the doctor today... i do indeed have strept throat... and if its not strept throat, then its mono (haha how much would that suck... i wonder who else would get it.. it would be a total domino effect) anyways they gave me this shot in my thigh.. the fucking nurse comes in with this huge needle and says "this is going to hurt" ?? you dont say that to your patient... but it did hurt.. and it was like 5 minutes long. and no one was there to hold my hand.. except my mommy. and i almost cried because i was scared. im a baby like that. i think im going to go back to bed.
so i guess we're doen with that whole talking thing.

i want a passion. im so sick of feeling like im doing nothing with my life. like that oh so typical question "what are your hobbies".. uhh... when everything in life gets shitty and boring, i want something to fall back on. an escape. i want to have something that i care about. actually.. im passionate about my friends. my best friends. they never cease to amaze me or brighten my day. the only times i feel depressed is when they arent by my side. fuck those days that i dont see them. however.. i need more than that. i need something to do. maybe ill dance.. or be a life gaurd join an organization that actually stands for something important. .. any ideas? this is one of those times i need my best friends. they can be productive with me.

.e.m.p.t.i.n.e.s.s.


ive never felt so lost and alone

i totally had a present on the doorstep when i got home.

ashley i love you more than the fucking universe.

i cant love anyone.
its all about the game.
the only way i can care about someone is if they dont care about me.
ill never change.
and ill always be alone.
whether or not someone is by my side.

i swallow hard
because i know
that what comes next will hurt
(you more than me)
i bite my lip
to try to stop it from shaking
the teeth have broken the skin
and the blood taste cold to me
after all
those nights you kept me warm
id hold my breath just to hear you sleep.
i must admit
i saw it coming
the air between us
had gotten harder yet to breath
id run away
if i could help it
but i cant remember to forget your face
you can say
my heart has changed
but its my will youve beaten down
id kiss you now
but i fear my caustic tongue
would only serve to salt your wounds
you are as beautiful as ever
but im starting to resent your smile
because its killing me 
to say this
but im dying inside to leave
its a place weve never been
its a waste to keep it in
it means little to you
means the world to me.

i really like him.

at this point he seems pretty much perfect, and as everyone tells me, hes exactly what i need right now...

but last night i realized for the first time in awhile that im not over it. 

its not love.. im not even sure if its like.. all i know is that i still care.. i still miss it.. and i still worry. hell always be amazing, his hearts just not in the right place anymore, i guess it never was to begin with. it just kills me sometimes.. knowing everything weve been through, and that we couldnt be farther apart. and knowing even more that it has to stay that way. he will always be incredible, its so hard seeing him throw it all away. i hate knowing that i wasnt enough to change him... that if we could have been different, everything would have been perfect.. but its not, and i am over us.. im over waiting on someone who will never love me enough.. and killing myself over someone who will never change.


my life is officially perfect. i can honestly say i wouldnt change a thing.

i want to sleepover at logs tonight. not work. 


those nights you kept me warm...
id hold my breath just to hear you sleep.

ive been so happy lately

everything seems close to perfect

<3 <3 <3 loggy i love you <3 <3 <3
